data.description: Wonderful home in a great Perry Hall setting features approximately 2464 total square feet. Recent updates include a new roof in 2020 and updated Primary Bath in 2019. First floor Family Room has sliding glass doors to the deck and patio, overlooking the fully fenced yard with a storage shed. Wood floors throughout the home. Upstairs there are four spacious bedrooms plus two full bathrooms. Lower level Rec Room offers many options, along with plenty of storage space. Walk-out stairs from the lower level to the side yard. 1 year Home Warranty covers all systems of the house for 1 year after settlement. All appliances included. Excellent opportunity!
